<h3 class="date"><a href="/2011/apr/26/">&#x27a0;</a> April 26, 2011</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="are-you-following-bot" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2011/05/are-you-following-a-bot/8448/">Are You Following a Bot?</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Atlantic article on the Web Ecology Project&#8217;s ace Socialbots game, where teams of software bots &#8220;played&#8221; to influence regular Twitter users.</p>

<p>“There’s a lot of potential for a lot of evil here,” admits Hwang. “But there’s also a lot of potential for a lot of good.”</p>

