    <div class="well" id="instagram" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://instagr.am/">instagr.am</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Like this app a lot. Best way to describe it is &#8220;Visual Twitter&#8221;. Crazy simple to quickly snap and share a photo, and get a stream of what your friends are up to.  (Also: fellow Dogpatch Labs residents, and Mike is on the Awesome Foundation SF board.)</p>

