<h3 class="date"><a href="/2009/oct/30/">&#x27a0;</a> October 30, 2009</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="darpa-network-challenge" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://networkchallenge.darpa.mil/">DARPA Network Challenge</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>This is a perfectly fascinating piece of research.  In much the same way as the NSA&#8217;s key-cracking competitions helped measure that state of the art in distributed computing, DARPA is running a contest that will help measure how social software and the internet can power a (really) wide area treasure hunt.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
                        : <a rel="tag" class="tag" href="/tag/darpa/">darpa</a>
                    
