<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Aardvark</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/3359502732/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Aardvark" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3006/3359502732_edb25198cc_m.jpg" height="240" width="199" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>My first interaction with <a href="http://vark.com/">Aardvark</a>.  I figured that sending it out at 1am meant I was unlikely to receive a response, much less a helpful one.  I was wrong.  Colour me impressed!</p>
        </p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
