        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://laughingsquid.com/burger-king-says-sacrifice-10-facebook-friends-for-a-whopper/">Burger King Says Sacrifice 10 Facebook Friends For a Whopper</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Brilliant piece of viral marketing by BK.  People will happily sell out their friends (and plaster BK&#8217;s name across their friend feeds) for a $3 hamburger.</p>

